@Tavaritz:


You've always been able to tap a tapped creature. It just has no effect. Ex: I [Enervate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Enervate) your *Birds of Paradise*. You tap it for mana while it's still on the stack. It's not countered, and I still get to draw a card.


The "untapped" in "tap an untapped creature" is not superfluous.
